### Anti-patterns (condensed — see 03-ANTI-PATTERNS.md for details)

18. **NEVER `Command::new("claude")`** — use `ModelCallService` / `ModelCaller` trait.
19. **NEVER `format!("You are the...")`** — use `PromptAssemblyService` / `SystemPromptBuilder`.
